Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比之前減少了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好趨勢
