Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部機體出發完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 做好著陸準備哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
