Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忍不住打哈欠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色新型機好像還沒有出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主機即將到達臨界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,valiancer隊立刻回艦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 請回艦
