Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等你這句話了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預想的一樣呢
