Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是佐基利亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾弗里德·加蘭特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊逼而來的是他們的部隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左翼發動機短艙中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是nectar來福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,valiancer可以攜帶的nectar炮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然配備到了前線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次2連射是極限了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐基利亞國防軍之星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝備了新兵器而來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可趕不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高速度無法恢復 甩不掉
