Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說 我們也正在去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有逃走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻做的不錯 野牛
