Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰果這才要顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 Cygnus很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們由我們來阻止
