Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥空域的聯結 時機非常苛刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請注意 青葉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意的話也可以放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LUXON 請求出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 是另一台新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛 就像你聽到的那樣 不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到可以聯結的區域還有15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還要和他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧 迪奧
