Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯結了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野牛 敵人…
