Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
